ygData.messageBody:
Aiyo Alex!

I think we have this huge communication problem. <grins widely> This the second time liaw. Hahaha! I am at the Karanas still....I dare not take on HighHold Pass alone. A LvL16 Cleric ask me to stay away until at least LvL15. However, I'd be taking the risk on Sat and try to go there with my best friend.

He managed to kill a LvL20+ Skele that conned red to him with a help of a cleric. He gained HALF a Tube/Bubble. Shoik man! Too bad I went to sleep liaw....was like 6am <grins>

Take care!
Wilson
